{"tid":438654,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[推廣+討論] 連登有冇人聽ムック(MUCC)啊?","createTime":"2017-10-17T06:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T15:50:39.000Z","uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ffcdbc81a0299ba4730750a3d1393458b16a5cb","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T06:31:28.000Z","msg":"連登好似冇人討論過，想搵下同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.syncmusic.jp/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mucc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.syncmusic.jp%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F05%2Fmucc.jpg&h=f09d06f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEdit from Wiki:<br />\n<strong>1997年2月以逹瑯與MIYA兩個人為中心組成的茨城縣樂隊MUCC。2000年8月14日團名正式改成ムック。2003年5月21日發行單曲「我、在ルベキ場所」後便正式浮上枱面。<br />\n<br />\n目前成員主要以結他手兼隊長MIYA、主唱逹瑯、鼓手SATOchi、貝斯手YUKKE所組成。剛出道的MUCC曲風融合了昭和時代的歌謠曲風，社會諷刺以及以「死」與「絕望」為歌名的歌詞佔大多數。從第三張專輯《鵬翼》開始，增加了Metal、Punk、Funk、Disco Beat等音樂要素，樂風更寬廣，但其音樂本質依然強烈。</strong><br />\n<br />\n好鍾意佢哋00年代啲牒，《是空》充滿實驗感但愈聽愈正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1kFbKxq-auE&amp;list=PL02DBF17D10EB807E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1kFbKxq-auE%26list%3DPL02DBF17D10EB807E&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a92fb4c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1kFbKxq-auE&amp;list=PL02DBF17D10EB807E</a><br />\n<br />\n到《朽木の灯》真係巔峰，上半隻牒啲一氣呵成感冇得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(雖然下半隻好散修修，呢個好似係佢哋嗰陣嘅通病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Bx-H6i0iPA&amp;list=PLIi-9naG_HhH7k_jxRHSkg3r1PQEp3gDf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6Bx-H6i0iPA%26list%3DPLIi-9naG_HhH7k_jxRHSkg3r1PQEp3gDf&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=dee786e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Bx-H6i0iPA&amp;list=PLIi-9naG_HhH7k_jxRHSkg3r1PQEp3gDf</a><br />\n<br />\n《志恩》啲民族風都好得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mkQEMBhNoTI&amp;list=PLFE3DF40DD6BE8A72\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmkQEMBhNoTI%26list%3DPLFE3DF40DD6BE8A72&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8aa79fb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mkQEMBhNoTI&amp;list=PLFE3DF40DD6BE8A72</a><br />\n<br />\n去到《球體》變得普通咗，但《hanabi》都屬於愈聽愈有味道嘅歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eFnEOwhb1BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeFnEOwhb1BA&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=715aa1c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eFnEOwhb1BA</a><br />\n<br />\n但後期轉玩Disco風就冇再追了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近聽下新版《Homura Uta》覺得逹瑯唱得好似Hea咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可能老屎忽情懷，覺得當年個版本好啲。<br />\n舊版：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sxIzQ4goPic&amp;list=PL6B07E3D81D73D74E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsxIzQ4goPic%26list%3DPL6B07E3D81D73D74E&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=b837c44c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sxIzQ4goPic&amp;list=PL6B07E3D81D73D74E</a><br />\n新版：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wYH9SZQQlec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwYH9SZQQlec&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=bf7294eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wYH9SZQQlec</a><br />\n<br />\n今年20週年，剛剛公佈出年年頭作有限期休息。希望休息完後新作品可以俾返少少舊作帶黎嘅Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb1bbc4ec7e7d837a6a2d7c7ff477b7d4d676f2","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"講下團員先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>Vocal: 逹瑯</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/899980636387016704/DA2NGjL2_400x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2F899980636387016704%2FDA2NGjL2_400x400.jpg&h=a292068e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nModel身形，但公認醜樣，兼夾把聲同台風都超級騎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但正因把聲係咁，唱密室系絕望系歌曲超有feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普遍Mukka（MUCC fans通稱）一見到佢就會毒舌mode發動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但藝術細胞，畫功了得，唔少官方illustration／goods都由佢操刀<br />\n<img src=\"https://shopping.deli-a.jp/images/Item/Item_UUEwfAxXukKq3ASasahIZ2w7R6ui33NB_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshopping.deli-a.jp%2Fimages%2FItem%2FItem_UUEwfAxXukKq3ASasahIZ2w7R6ui33NB_1.jpg&h=721d25f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Guitar: MIYA (ミヤ)</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/8e/9e/ec/8e9eec07f394fd1ef9d4fd9d72c0c79c--visual-kei-pastels.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F8e%2F9e%2Fec%2F8e9eec07f394fd1ef9d4fd9d72c0c79c--visual-kei-pastels.jpg&h=447965ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMUCC入面我最鍾意的團員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  人仔細細，但氣場逼人，簡直可以用眼神殺死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n和音多數佢負責，雖然聲底好薄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順帶一提佢算係俾音樂浸大，媽媽係音樂老師，《球體》入面首《讚美歌》把女聲就係MIYA媽唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q6ika7iVgzA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQ6ika7iVgzA&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8a376f90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q6ika7iVgzA</a><br />\n(sor我搵唔到CD版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"18037a0d316dd309dd0568e7d1b23555372c2529","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>BASS: YUKKE</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/6c/83/10/6c831030aff4cd226b9e7b49fd6fda1b--festival-visual-kei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F6c%2F83%2F10%2F6c831030aff4cd226b9e7b49fd6fda1b--festival-visual-kei.jpg&h=b201bb69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBand中嘅口水佬(尤其喺官方blog度寧舍多嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n又會好變態地分身做一個叫「輸血子」嘅女角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特徵係金色頭(雖然而家唔再係蘑菇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )+達瑯嘅玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但好多人都係因為非常濃重嘅bassline而留意MUCC，YUKKE功不可沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時LIVE中YUKKE會用一把好似大提琴嘅BASS，彈起上來好迷人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d2zE736z7Pk&amp;list=RDd2zE736z7Pk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dd2zE736z7Pk%26list%3DRDd2zE736z7Pk&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=2b806be1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d2zE736z7Pk&amp;list=RDd2zE736z7Pk</a>"},{"pid":"4437da4ee80a053faa91a29cfedad0684b1f627b","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:07:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>Drums: SATOchi</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://ic.pics.livejournal.com/sbeec/33227706/8488/8488_640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fic.pics.livejournal.com%2Fsbeec%2F33227706%2F8488%2F8488_640.jpg&h=7b994a87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條友我唔識點介紹佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然係個靚仔，但真係一個蠢蛋嚟，講嘢成日9唔搭8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlive打鼓嗰陣個口會不自覺郁下郁下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又好有魅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5vF7eQ3UGZo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5vF7eQ3UGZo&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=10c01050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5vF7eQ3UGZo</a>"},{"pid":"3573e19304bbbd9370a348ede1aa3fc2a3a64954","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"有聽過或者鍾意佢地嘅一齊傾下計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0572c89ec01eb1dc37b7946d73d62d6b49e49352","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T10:14:21.000Z","msg":"冇人聽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6705ef51e7f0b44a873788597ed5e11d90f64dba","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e086fc9dfabb6355f390711dd16137b521554ab0","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f4265ae6b2e1fbb55b2e7a472c5626ba6bdc37","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26817515ca51fb3aaabb3efe565d8130785508b1","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93b2ae8e32fb91def42fa82d092fc9cb69d1004","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:21:11.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd33530f656138bb0cd4d161d2388990ae0c2863","tid":438654,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:16:03.000Z","msg":"有聽頭幾隻碟<br />\n最鍾意哀愁"},{"pid":"02665e0a9a728ff7677394c964eb9ff1c458157b","tid":438654,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:41:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>BASS: YUKKE</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/6c/83/10/6c831030aff4cd226b9e7b49fd6fda1b--festival-visual-kei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F6c%2F83%2F10%2F6c831030aff4cd226b9e7b49fd6fda1b--festival-visual-kei.jpg&h=b201bb69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBand中嘅口水佬(尤其喺官方blog度寧舍多嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n又會好變態地分身做一個叫「輸血子」嘅女角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特徵係金色頭(雖然而家唔再係蘑菇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )+達瑯嘅玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但好多人都係因為非常濃重嘅bassline而留意MUCC，YUKKE功不可沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時LIVE中YUKKE會用一把好似大提琴嘅BASS，彈起上來好迷人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d2zE736z7Pk&amp;list=RDd2zE736z7Pk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dd2zE736z7Pk%26list%3DRDd2zE736z7Pk&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=2b806be1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d2zE736z7Pk&amp;list=RDd2zE736z7Pk</a>&amp;list=RDd2zE736z7Pk</blockquote><br />\nMucc 啲bass 堅好聽"},{"pid":"4c70d1dc26b90633236d9916cd96f558661f0053","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有聽頭幾隻碟<br />\n最鍾意哀愁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你覆啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新作真係聽唔返舊作既feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad32dd8dd6f9947c2c3bc7033685889b5d83003b","tid":438654,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T02:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有聽頭幾隻碟<br />\n最鍾意哀愁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你覆啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新作真係聽唔返舊作既feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有買新葬x軀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係鍾意舊聲多啲"},{"pid":"28a79b5187edce4cd7474d831e81d79562bb7afe","tid":438654,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T02:32:02.000Z","msg":"主音歐陽震華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽過少少，之前重錄果2隻初期ALBUM幾好聽<br />\n仲有Mr.Liar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係查過吓D資料，隊嘢編曲9成都係MIYA做，其他人做緊乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f483acf3aca2b0bfb82eebf23cfbe863d81e9919","tid":438654,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T02:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有聽頭幾隻碟<br />\n最鍾意哀愁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你覆啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新作真係聽唔返舊作既feel<img src=\"/assets/